    The valid combinations of AccountRestrictionFlag that creates a AccountRestrictionFlags. Type of account restriction types: 0x0001 (1 decimal) - Allow only incoming transactions from a given address. 0x0002 (2 decimal) - Allow only incoming transactions containing a given mosaic identifier. 0x4001 (16385 decimal) - Allow only outgoing transactions to a given address. 0x4004 (16388 decimal) - Allow only outgoing transactions with a given transaction type. 0x8001 (32769 decimal) - Block incoming transactions from a given address. 0x8002 (32770 decimal) - Block incoming transactions containing a given mosaic identifier. 0xC001 (49153 decimal) - Block outgoing transactions to a given address. 0xC004 (49156 decimal) - Block outgoing transactions with a given transaction type.
